{"tid":1821931,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Keroro 有冇機會再出動畫版??","createTime":"2020-01-12T15:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T15:39:16.000Z","uid":258706,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1e30688751ebda90a6238470cd0bd8c7d27720c5","tid":1821931,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"中、小學果陣好鍾意睇 Keroro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但2012年度播出動畫版第七季最尾集之後，就一直冇出新動畫... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人知Keroro有冇機會再出返新動畫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好想再有新既睇<br />\n另外，聽講動畫版冇出後漫畫版仍然出緊<br />\n不過咁多年我一直冇追漫畫版，因為唔知邊度有得睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲知邊度有Keroro漫畫 (中文版) 可以網上睇/有實體書可以買黎睇?"},{"pid":"fd1a00f204b461d4fc6497ad603388162b27a8f6","tid":1821931,"uid":216354,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"過去既野留係記憶最美好<br />\n<br />\n你搵返出黎睇就會唔再鍾意"},{"pid":"1d2058cb99ce036535e9a8c331e448624e3a3421","tid":1821931,"uid":36915,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"14年出過flash版評價比人屌到飛起<br />\n日昇賺毒撚錢好過<br />\nKeroro 可以算係90至00後集體回憶<br />\n紅過七年作品已經好難得"},{"pid":"dcad84b6dbd3eb7e8e280a66b73c67e39eb968f6","tid":1821931,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"tvb頭果50集配音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d77f50cf5a4fafd78eeb21b2cec516d9702acb","tid":1821931,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:57:20.000Z","msg":"漫畫中文版都冇再出啦 大陸漢化都冇人做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f483e9280181bff58e83bfdef2a2d7465122d4","tid":1821931,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2058cb99ce036535e9a8c331e4486